posts.post_title: FT: Wiltse with cap Blank Back - PULLED
posts.post_content:
9/18 - Pulling this card for now.  
++++++

Offering this Wiltse blank back for trade before I send him off to SGC.  Card is super cool and unique, being listed as unconfirmed in t206resource.  Card also has the cool red face ghosting.  

You can also see the remnants of a wet sheet transfer of his face and his buttons on the back.

Anyway, entertaining offers for graded HOFers and EPDG’s, especially ones I need or which would be upgrades for my current group. Will also consider trades for SILVER and GOLD.  Just let me know what you have.

Shoot me a PM.

Thanks for looking!

Anyway, if anyone is interested in trading for this guy, please let me know.
